OL,3,CFinancial pressure leads to ward
OL,4,Cclosure
OL,6,FA hospital has been forced to close
OL,7,Fone of its wards due to the "real-
OL,8,Fworld impact" of financial pressures.
OL,10,FThe Cuerden ward, at Chorley and South
OL,11,FRibble Hospital, is a 24 bed facility
OL,12,Fthat provides additional space for
OL,13,Fdiabetes, endocrinology and other
OL,14,Fgeneral medical patients.
OL,16,FThe ward opened in July 2022, but will
OL,17,Fnow close in March 2025.
