OL,6,FConfirming the closure Lancashire
OL,7,FTeaching Hospitals NHS Foundation
OL,8,FTrust (LTH) said it was part of the
OL,9,Fprocess of 'flexing' how many beds are
OL,10,Fopen according to demand, which is
OL,11,Fgreatest during the winter.
OL,13,FThe boss of the trust said the closure
OL,14,Fis among the "real-world impacts" of
OL,15,Fthe financial difficulties facing the
OL,16,Forganisation.
