OL,6,FSilas Nicholls, LTH chief executive,
OL,7,Facknowledged at a board meeting on
OL,8,FThursday that the "difficult decision"
OL,9,Falso had its roots in the budgetary
OL,10,Fpressure the trust is under.
OL,12,FLTH has already been placed by NHS
OL,13,FEngland into the equivalent of
OL,14,Ffinancial special measures along with
OL,15,Fits counterparts in Blackpool, East
OL,16,FLancashire and the overarching
OL,17,FLancashire and South Cumbria
OL,18,FIntegrated Care Board. All of those
OL,19,Forganisations will now be subject to
OL,20,F"intensive support" to recover their
OL,21,Ffinancial positions.
