OL,3,CFinancial pressure leads to ward
OL,4,Cclosure
OL,6,F"The Cuerden ward itself is actually
OL,7,Freally good estate so...what we'll be
OL,8,Flooking at is what else we can move
OL,9,Finto that space" he said.
OL,11,FThe board was told there were also
OL,12,Ffewer patients being referred to
OL,13,FCuerden beds from the Preston area,
OL,14,Fbecause of the opening of the acute
OL,15,Fmedical unit at the Royal.
